5
00:00:24,228 --> 00:00:25,640
You're going with dad, right, grandma?

6
00:00:27,465 --> 00:00:28,809
What's wrong, grandma?

7
00:00:30,896 --> 00:00:34,101
You're not saying I have to choose by myself, right?

8
00:00:34,570 --> 00:00:36,709
That'd be a tough call for me.

9
00:00:38,078 --> 00:00:40,015
Ton gets to be with dad,

10
00:00:40,783 --> 00:00:42,601
Tung gets to be with mom

11
00:00:43,029 --> 00:00:45,637
Why should I be the one who gets to choose?

12
00:00:58,001 --> 00:01:00,403
Your mom and dad just part ways

13
00:01:01,021 --> 00:01:04,081
It's tough for both of them.

14
00:01:06,741 --> 00:01:08,081
And...

15
00:01:08,292 --> 00:01:11,816
When they're trying to settle down again

16
00:01:13,321 --> 00:01:16,078
It'd be tough to bring two children along.

17
00:01:17,998 --> 00:01:20,080
Let's wait until they're settled.

18
00:01:25,469 --> 00:01:26,508
Alright?

19
00:01:29,123 --> 00:01:30,077
Yes

20
00:01:30,572 --> 00:01:32,077
It's fine.

21
00:01:33,001 --> 00:01:35,903
You must listen to my word from now on, alright?

22
00:01:36,409 --> 00:01:38,708
So you wouldn't be a problematic child.

23
00:01:40,235 --> 00:01:41,901
And stay within the line.

24
00:01:43,709 --> 00:01:44,607
Yes

25
00:02:05,877 --> 00:02:08,001
Get down here and help me with work.

26
00:02:08,930 --> 00:02:10,509
What on earth are you doing?

27
00:02:10,746 --> 00:02:12,745
Make your life worthy of some good.

28
00:02:12,975 --> 00:02:16,001
Don't just lie there and daydream.

29
00:02:16,221 --> 00:02:18,001
Or watch some silly videos.

30
00:02:18,009 --> 00:02:20,001
Did you hear me?

